import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data[['Bacteria', 'Penicillin', 'Genus']]
    chart = sns.boxplot(x='Genus', y='Penicillin', data=data)
    chart.set_xticklabels(chart.get_xticklabels(), rotation=45, horizontalalignment='right')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of Penicillin across different Bacteria Genus?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data[['Streptomycin', 'Neomycin', 'Gram_Staining']]
    data = data.groupby(['Gram_Staining']).mean().reset_index()
    data = pd.melt(data, id_vars=['Gram_Staining'], value_vars=['Streptomycin', 'Neomycin'], var_name='Antibiotic', value_name='Effectiveness')
    chart = sns.catplot(x='Gram_Staining', y='Effectiveness', hue='Antibiotic', data=data, kind='bar')
    plt.title('How does the effectiveness of Streptomycin compare to Neomycin?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data[['Bacteria', 'Gram_Staining', 'Genus']]
    data = data.groupby(['Bacteria', 'Gram_Staining']).count().reset_index()
    data = data.pivot(index='Bacteria', columns='Gram_Staining', values='Genus')
    data = data.fillna(0)
    data = data.div(data.sum(axis=1), axis=0)
    data.plot(kind='bar', stacked=True)
    plt.title('What is the distribution of Gram Staining across different Bacteria Genus?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend(title='Gram Staining', loc='center left', bbox_to_anchor=(1.0, 0.5))
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
